    <body.head>
      <hedline>
        <hl1>Your Kids Are Their Problem</hl1>
      </hedline>
      <abstract>
        <p>Rev Bruce M Shipman letter on Lisa Belkin's July 23 article is distressed that people like Jason Gill are unwilling to join village in raising children</p>
      </abstract>
    </body.head>
    <body.content>
      <block class="lead_paragraph">
        <p>If there's more than a modicum of truth in your article, the national community is in danger of ever-greater balkanization. It does take a village to raise a child, and it disturbs me that people like Jason Gill want no part in it.</p>
        <p>The Rev. Bruce M.  Shipman  Groton, Conn.</p>
      </block>
